umontreal.iro.lecuyer.probdist

Class ConstantDist

  • java.lang.Object
    • umontreal.iro.lecuyer.probdist.DiscreteDistribution
      • umontreal.iro.lecuyer.probdist.ConstantDist
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Distribution

    public class ConstantDist
extends DiscreteDistribution
    Extends the class DiscreteDistribution for a constant discrete distribution taking a single real value with probability 1. Its mass function is

    p(x) = 1,        for x = c,

    and p(x) = 0 elsewhere.
